## Summary: Profile URL Extraction in search.py

I've found all the code related to extracting `profile_url` from search results. Here's the complete breakdown:

### 1. **CandidateBasic Dataclass** (Lines 69-80)
```python
@dataclass
class CandidateBasic:
    """Basic candidate information from search results."""
    maimai_id: str
    name: str
    title: str
    company: str
    location: Optional[str] = None
    profile_url: Optional[str] = None  # вЖР Line 77

    def to_dict(self) -> dict:
        return asdict(self)
```

### 2. **Main Extraction Function: `_extract_search_results`** (Lines 231-625)

This is the PRIMARY function that extracts search results and profile URLs. It contains:

#### **A) JavaScript-based extraction** (Lines 252-480)
The core logic uses `page.evaluate()` to run JavaScript that extracts candidates. Key lines:

**Extract contactcard DOM to get user ID (Lines 371-407):**
```javascript
// Lines 371-417: Extract user ID from contactcard_{user_id} pattern
let userId = '';
let el = card;
while (el) {
    const elId = el.id || '';
    const ccMatch = elId.match(/^contactcard_(\d+)$/);  // Line 376
    if (ccMatch) {
        userId = ccMatch[1];
        break;
    }
    el = el.parentElement;
}
// Also check descendants for the contactcard pattern
if (!userId) {
    const ccEl = card.querySelector('[id^="contactcard_"]');  // Line 385
    if (ccEl) {
        const ccMatch = ccEl.id.match(/^contactcard_(\d+)$/);  // Line 387
        if (ccMatch) {
            userId = ccMatch[1];
        }
    }
}
```

**Build profile URL from user ID (Lines 413-417):**
```javascript
// Build profile URL from user ID when available
let profileUrl = '';
if (userId) {
    profileUrl = 'https://maimai.cn/contact/detail/' + userId + '?dstu=' + userId;  // Line 416
}
```

**Fallback: Extract profile URL from `<a>` tags (Lines 419-453):**
```javascript
// Fallback: extract profile URL from <a> tags inside the card
if (!profileUrl) {
    let fallbackUrl = '';

    // First: check <a> ancestors between img and card
    let ancestor = img.parentElement;
    while (ancestor && ancestor !== card) {
        if (ancestor.tagName === 'A' && ancestor.href) {
            const href = ancestor.getAttribute('href') || '';
            if (href.includes('/profile/detail') || href.includes('/contact/detail/') 
                || href.includes('/u/') || href.includes('egid=') || href.includes('dstu=')) {
                profileUrl = href.startsWith('http') ? href : 'https://maimai.cn' + href;  // Line 429
                break;
            }
        }
        ancestor = ancestor.parentElement;
    }

    // Second: search all <a> descendants inside the card
    if (!profileUrl) {
        const links = card.querySelectorAll('a[href]');  // Line 438
        for (const link of links) {
            const href = link.getAttribute('href') || '';
            if (href.includes('/profile/detail') || href.includes('/contact/detail/') 
                || href.includes('/u/') || href.includes('egid=') || href.includes('dstu=')) {
                profileUrl = href.startsWith('http') ? href : 'https://maimai.cn' + href;  // Line 442
                break;
            }
            if (!fallbackUrl && href && !href.startsWith('javascript:') 
                && (href.startsWith('/') || href.includes('maimai.cn'))) {
                fallbackUrl = href.startsWith('http') ? href : 'https://maimai.cn' + href;  // Line 446
            }
        }
    }
    if (!profileUrl && fallbackUrl) {
        profileUrl = fallbackUrl;  // Line 451
    }
}
```

**Return profile_url in candidate object (Line 474):**
```javascript
candidates.push({
    name: name,
    title: title || '',
    company: company || '',
    maimai_id: maimaiId,
    profile_url: profileUrl,  // вЖР Line 474
